{"id":11771,"date":"2025-03-14T18:06:12","date_gmt":"2025-03-14T11:06:12","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/?p=11771"},"modified":"2025-03-14T18:57:46","modified_gmt":"2025-03-14T11:57:46","slug":"san-golf-vinpearl-golf-leman-cu-chi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/san-golf-vinpearl-golf-leman-cu-chi\/","title":{"rendered":"S\u00e2n Golf Vinpearl Golf L\u00e9man C\u1ee7 Chi"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vinpearl Golf L\u00e9man, c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi t\u00ean g\u1ecdi S\u00e2n golf C\u1ee7 Chi ho\u1eb7c S\u00e2n golf Nh\u00e2n S\u01b0, l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Vingroup, d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 3\/2025. Vinpearl Golf L\u00e9man C\u1ee7 Chi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n s\u00e2n Golf v\u00e0 khu ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1edbi n\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i C\u1ee7 Chi, TP. H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh, thu\u1ed9c qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd c\u1ee7a VinGroup qua th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u Vinpearl, n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c khu ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u00e0 ti\u1ec7n \u00edch cao c\u1ea5p.<\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh v\u00e0 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed ra \u0111\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Vinpearl Golf L\u00e9man<\/h2>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ef1 \u00e1n n\u00e0y ban \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi t\u00ean S\u00e2n golf CT Sphinx tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ed5i th\u00e0nh L\u00e9man Golf, v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u00e0 Vinpearl Golf L\u00e9man d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Vingroup. V\u1edbi kho\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 42,6 tri\u1ec7u USD, s\u00e2n golf n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m golf t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c ph\u00eda t\u00e2y TP. H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh.<\/div>\n<div>\u00a0<\/div>\n<div>\n<div id=\"attachment_11772\" style=\"width: 1210px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11772\" class=\"wp-image-11772 size-full lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/san-golf-vinpearl-folf-leman-cu-chi.jpg\" alt=\"S\u00e2n Golf Vinpearl Golf L\u00e9man C\u1ee7 Chi\" width=\"1200\" height=\"754\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 1200px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 1200\/754;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11772\" class=\"wp-image-11772 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/san-golf-vinpearl-folf-leman-cu-chi.jpg\" alt=\"S\u00e2n Golf Vinpearl Golf L\u00e9man C\u1ee7 Chi\" width=\"1200\" height=\"754\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-11772\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">S\u00e2n Golf Vinpearl Golf L\u00e9man C\u1ee7 Chi<\/p><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o n\u0103m 2018, Vinhomes (thu\u1ed9c VinGroup) \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e2u t\u00f3m 98% c\u1ed5 ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ty n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u s\u1ef1 chuy\u1ec3n giao qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd sang VinGroup. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do s\u00e2n golf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eafn v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u Vinpearl, n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c s\u00e2n golf v\u00e0 khu ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Vinpearl Golf H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng, Nam H\u1ed9i An, Nha Trang, v\u00e0 Ph\u00fa Qu\u1ed1c.<\/p>\n<table style=\"width: 98.955%; height: 216px;\">\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"height: 24px;\">\n<th style=\"height: 24px;\">Danh m\u1ee5c<\/th>\n<th style=\"height: 24px;\">Chi ti\u1ebft<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 24px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 24px;\">T\u00ean g\u1ecdi<\/td>\n<td style=\"height: 24px;\">Vinpearl Golf L\u00e9man C\u1ee7 Chi (c\u00f2n g\u1ecdi S\u00e2n golf C\u1ee7 Chi, S\u00e2n golf Nh\u00e2n S\u01b0)<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 24px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 24px;\">V\u1ecb tr\u00ed<\/td>\n<td style=\"height: 24px;\">Qu\u1ed1c l\u1ed9 22, T\u00e2n Th\u00f4ng H\u1ed9i, Huy\u1ec7n C\u1ee7 Chi, TP. H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 24px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 24px;\">Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch<\/td>\n<td style=\"height: 24px;\">200 ha<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 24px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 24px;\">S\u1ed1 l\u1ed7<\/td>\n<td style=\"height: 24px;\">36 l\u1ed7 ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 24px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 24px;\">Chi\u1ec1u d\u00e0i<\/td>\n<td style=\"height: 24px;\">7.688 yards<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 24px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 24px;\">Lo\u1ea1i c\u1ecf<\/td>\n<td style=\"height: 24px;\">Paspalum (gi\u1ea3m h\u00f3a ch\u1ea5t, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p kh\u00ed h\u1eadu nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1edbi)<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 24px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 24px;\">H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng tho\u00e1t n\u01b0\u1edbc<\/td>\n<td style=\"height: 24px;\">\u0110\u1ea1t chu\u1ea9n ch\u00e2u \u00c2u<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 24px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 24px;\">Nh\u00e0 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf<\/td>\n<td style=\"height: 24px;\">Brian Curley v\u00e0 Lee Schmidt, n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng khu v\u1ef1c ch\u00e2u \u00c1 &#8211; Th\u00e1i B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0<\/div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u00e2n Golf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng theo ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng Golfer trong v\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i n\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/div>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u00e2n Golf<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u00e2n golf n\u1eb1m t\u1ea1i Qu\u1ed1c l\u1ed9 22, T\u00e2n Th\u00f4ng H\u1ed9i, Huy\u1ec7n C\u1ee7 Chi, TP. H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh, m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf ph\u00eda T\u00e2y th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1. Kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch di chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi nh\u1eadn nh\u01b0 sau:<\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li>20 ph\u00fat t\u1eeb B\u00ecnh Th\u1ea1nh<\/li>\n<li>25 ph\u00fat t\u1eeb Th\u1ea3o \u0110i\u1ec1n (Qu\u1eadn 2)<\/li>\n<li>30 ph\u00fat t\u1eeb s\u00e2n bay T\u00e2n S\u01a1n Nh\u1ea5t<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t Vinpearl Golf Leman l\u00e0 1 d\u1ef1 \u00e1n th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb Vinhomes C\u1ee7 Chi, n\u1ebfu qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a d\u1ef1 \u00e1n n\u00e0y th\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham kh\u1ea3o t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y: <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/vinhomes-cu-chi\/\">VINHOMES C\u1ee6 CHI<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_11779\" style=\"width: 1210px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11779\" class=\"wp-image-11779 size-full lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/vi-tri-vinpearl-golf-leman.jpg\" alt=\"V\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u00e2n Vinpearl Golf Leman C\u1ee7 Chi\" width=\"1200\" height=\"811\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 1200px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 1200\/811;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11779\" class=\"wp-image-11779 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/vi-tri-vinpearl-golf-leman.jpg\" alt=\"V\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u00e2n Vinpearl Golf Leman C\u1ee7 Chi\" width=\"1200\" height=\"811\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-11779\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">V\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u00e2n Vinpearl Golf Leman C\u1ee7 Chi<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n cho Golfer trong th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 m\u00e0 c\u00f2n h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u1edbi du kh\u00e1ch qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec3m du l\u1ecbch l\u00e2n c\u1eadn.<\/p>\n<div>\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, S\u00e2n Golf n\u1eb1m d\u1ecdc s\u00f4ng Th\u1ea7y Cai, n\u1ed1i li\u1ec1n s\u00f4ng S\u00e0i G\u00f2n v\u00e0 s\u00f4ng V\u00e0m C\u1ecf \u0110\u00f4ng, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao quanh b\u1edfi n\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf ba m\u1eb7t, t\u1ea1o n\u00ean khung c\u1ea3nh y\u00ean b\u00ecnh v\u00e0 th\u01a1 m\u1ed9ng.<\/div>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u00e0 \u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m S\u00e2n Golf<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u00e2n golf do Brian Curley v\u00e0 Lee Schmidt th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n, hai nh\u00e0 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u00e2n golf h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u khu v\u1ef1c ch\u00e2u \u00c1 &#8211; Th\u00e1i B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c T\u1ea1p Ch\u00ed Golf Ch\u00e2u \u00c1 b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2011 v\u00e0 2012. Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ecba h\u00ecnh t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c Fairway th\u1eed th\u00e1ch v\u00e0 c\u1ea3nh quan xanh m\u00e1t.<\/p>\n<div>S\u00e2n golf c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng di\u1ec7n t\u00edch 200 ha, c\u00f3 36 l\u1ed7, v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng chi\u1ec1u d\u00e0i 7.688 yards, \u0111\u1ecba h\u00ecnh t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea3nh quan t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, bao quanh b\u1edfi ba m\u1eb7t s\u00f4ng v\u00e0 39 h\u1ed3 l\u1edbn, t\u1ea1o n\u00ean khung c\u1ea3nh th\u01a1 m\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem\u00a0l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng s\u00e2n d\u00e0i nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u00e2n golf s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ecf Paspalum, lo\u1ea1i c\u1ecf hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, gi\u1ea3m nhu c\u1ea7u s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u00f3a ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi kh\u00ed h\u1eadu nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1edbi. H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng tho\u00e1t n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1t chu\u1ea9n ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t quanh n\u0103m. Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ecba h\u00ecnh t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, bao g\u1ed3m b\u1edd s\u00f4ng Th\u1ea7y Cai, n\u1ed1i li\u1ec1n s\u00f4ng S\u00e0i G\u00f2n v\u00e0 s\u00f4ng V\u00e0m C\u1ecf \u0110\u00f4ng, t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3nh quan y\u00ean b\u00ecnh v\u00e0 th\u01a1 m\u1ed9ng.<\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec7n \u00edch v\u00e0 C\u01a1 s\u1edf V\u1eadt ch\u1ea5t<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vinpearl Golf L\u00e9man C\u1ee7 Chi kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 s\u00e2n golf m\u00e0 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t khu ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n. C\u00e1c ti\u1ec7n \u00edch bao g\u1ed3m:<\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li>Bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 cho thu\u00ea: 200 c\u0103n, di\u1ec7n t\u00edch t\u1eeb 360m\u00b2 \u0111\u1ebfn 480m\u00b2, \u0111\u1ea1t ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n 5 sao, ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 thu\u00ea d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n.<\/li>\n<li>Nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng: M\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng 5 sao ven s\u00f4ng, mang l\u1ea1i tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m \u1ea9m th\u1ef1c cao c\u1ea5p.<\/li>\n<li>Spa: Spa sang tr\u1ecdng, \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nhu c\u1ea7u th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n c\u1ee7a du kh\u00e1ch.<\/li>\n<li>C\u1eeda h\u00e0ng: C\u00e1c c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng cao c\u1ea5p, ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 mua s\u1eafm.<\/li>\n<li>Khu vui ch\u01a1i tr\u1ebb em: \u0110\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nhu c\u1ea7u gia \u0111\u00ecnh, t\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng gian gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed cho tr\u1ebb.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, khu v\u1ef1c xung quanh c\u00f3 c\u00e1c ti\u1ec7n \u00edch ngo\u1ea1i vi nh\u01b0 nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng gia \u0111\u00ecnh H\u01b0\u01a1ng Tr\u00e0m Qu\u00e1n, v\u00e0 c\u1ea3nh quan s\u00f4ng n\u01b0\u1edbc, t\u0103ng th\u00eam gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng.<\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 T\u01b0\u01a1ng Lai<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u00e2n Golf \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c h\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5c cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn m\u1edf c\u1eeda khai tr\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 3\/2025. T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, s\u00e2n Golf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p nh\u1edd ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng th\u00eam n\u1ebfu k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch 36 l\u1ed7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n.<\/p>\n<p>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 03\/2025 v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Golf.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-11773 size-full lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/hinh-anh-thuc-te-san-golf-cu-chi-1.jpg\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf s\u00e2n golf 1\" width=\"1200\" height=\"666\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 1200px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 1200\/666;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-11773 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/hinh-anh-thuc-te-san-golf-cu-chi-1.jpg\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf s\u00e2n golf 1\" width=\"1200\" height=\"666\" \/><\/noscript> <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-11774 size-full lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/shinh-anh-thuc-te-san-gold-cu-chi-2.jpg\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf s\u00e2n golf 2\" width=\"1200\" height=\"673\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 1200px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 1200\/673;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-11774 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/shinh-anh-thuc-te-san-gold-cu-chi-2.jpg\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf s\u00e2n golf 2\" width=\"1200\" height=\"673\" \/><\/noscript> <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-11775 size-full lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/hinh-anh-thuc-te-san-golf-cu-chi-3.jpg\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf s\u00e2n golf 3\" width=\"1200\" height=\"671\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 1200px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 1200\/671;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-11775 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/hinh-anh-thuc-te-san-golf-cu-chi-3.jpg\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf s\u00e2n golf 3\" width=\"1200\" height=\"671\" \/><\/noscript> <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-11776 size-full lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/hinh-anh-thuc-te-san-golf-cu-chi-4.jpg\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf s\u00e2n golf 4\" width=\"1200\" height=\"667\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 1200px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 1200\/667;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-11776 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/hinh-anh-thuc-te-san-golf-cu-chi-4.jpg\" alt=\"H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf s\u00e2n golf 4\" width=\"1200\" height=\"667\" \/><\/noscript><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00e0y 14-02-2025 v\u1eeba qua t\u1ea1i C\u1ee7 Chi, Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 H\u1ed3 Chi \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra l\u1ec5 k\u00fd k\u1ebft tho\u1ea3 thu\u1eadn h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c gi\u1eefa Vinpearl v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c Pasiio Golf v\u00e0 F Golf \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh s\u00e2n Golf C\u1ee7 Chi.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-11777 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/ky-ket-hop-tac-vinpearl-va-passio-golf.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"899\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 1200px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 1200\/899;\"><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-11777\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/ky-ket-hop-tac-vinpearl-va-passio-golf.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"899\"><\/noscript> <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-11778 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/le-ky-ket-hop-tac-fgolf-vinpearl.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"910\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 1200px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 1200\/910;\"><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-11778\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/le-ky-ket-hop-tac-fgolf-vinpearl.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"910\"><\/noscript><\/p>\n<h2>Gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 v\u00e0 ph\u00ed d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u01a1i\u00a0<\/h2>\n<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e1 r\u01a1i d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 1.700.000 \u0111\u1ebfn 2.500.000 VN\u0110 v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 2.160.000 VN\u0110 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, do Vinpearl Golf C\u1ee7 Chi n\u1eb1m t\u1ea1i TP. H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh, n\u01a1i chi ph\u00ed sinh ho\u1ea1t v\u00e0 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 cao h\u01a1n, gi\u00e1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng l\u00ean, d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1eeb 2.500.000 \u0111\u1ebfn 3.500.000 VN\u0110 cho 18 l\u1ed7, bao g\u1ed3m ph\u00ed s\u00e2n, caddie v\u00e0 xe \u0111i\u1ec7n chung.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t sinh th\u00eam c\u00e1c chi ph\u00ed li\u00ean quan nh\u01b0:<\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li>Ph\u00ed s\u00e2n (green fee).<\/li>\n<li>Ph\u00ed caddie.<\/li>\n<li>Ph\u00ed xe \u0111i\u1ec7n chung (c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5 thu n\u1ebfu \u0111i l\u1ebb, kho\u1ea3ng 375.000 VN\u0110\/kh\u00e1ch.<\/li>\n<li>Ph\u1ee5 thu cho kh\u00e1ch n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i: 200.000 VN\u0110\/kh\u00e1ch.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c ti\u1ec7n \u00edch b\u1ed5 sung nh\u01b0 thu\u00ea g\u1eady, gi\u00e0y golf, ho\u1eb7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng spa, nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng s\u1ebd t\u00ednh th\u00eam.<\/p>\n<h2>Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb7t s\u00e2n Golf\u00a0<\/h2>\n<div>\n<ul class=\"marker:text-secondary\">\n<li class=\"break-words\">Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi Vinpearl Golf C\u1ee7 Chi qua c\u00e1c k\u00eanh nh\u01b0 Elinkgolf, n\u01a1i cung c\u1ea5p d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1eb7t s\u00e2n v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i.<\/li>\n<li class=\"break-words\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u1ed7 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Vinpearl t\u1ea1i booking.vinpearl.com, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 trang web hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb gi\u00e1 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<\/li>\n<li class=\"break-words\">Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00fd golf nh\u01b0 Alegolf \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 v\u00e0 \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ebft Lu\u1eadn<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vinpearl Golf L\u00e9man C\u1ee7 Chi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n \u0111\u1ea7y ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n Golf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 khu ngh\u1ec9 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng cao c\u1ea5p, h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho Golfer v\u00e0 du kh\u00e1ch. V\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i, thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, v\u00e0 ti\u1ec7n \u00edch \u0111a d\u1ea1ng, n\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m Golf t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u00e0 c\u00f2n g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n du l\u1ecbch khu v\u1ef1c ph\u00eda T\u00e2y TP. H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh.<\/p>\n<p>Xem th\u00eam c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin h\u1eefu \u00edch t\u1ea1i website: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/\">https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"kk-star-ratings kksr-auto kksr-align-right kksr-valign-bottom\"\n    data-payload='{&quot;align&quot;:&quot;right&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;11771&quot;,&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;default&quot;,&quot;valign&quot;:&quot;bottom&quot;,&quot;ignore&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;reference&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;count&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;legendonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;readonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;score&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;starsonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;best&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;gap&quot;:&quot;4&quot;,&quot;greet&quot;:&quot;\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft&